 body=f'<section class="hero circuit-shell"><div class="hero-copy"><p class="eyebrow">⚡ Galena-based electrical contractor</p><h1>Power work that feels planned before a wire gets touched.</h1><p class="hero-lede">JAG Electric handles residential and commercial electrical work around Galena, Pittsburg, and nearby communities — panel upgrades, rewiring, fixtures, outlets, remodel wiring, and clean troubleshooting.</p><div class="hero-actions"><a class="btn primary" href="tel:{tel}">Call {phone}</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/estimate-prep">Build an estimate-prep summary →</a></div><div class="proof-strip"><span>★ 4.9 Google rating / 50 reviews supplied</span><span>✓ BBB A+ / Accredited since 2020</span><span>✓ Free estimates listed on HomeAdvisor</span></div></div><div class="hero-photo-stack">{photo("panel","Electrical panel inspection and planning")}{photo("work","Electrician working at an electrical panel")}</div></section>'
